{"tid":1123211,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「利物浦」係最多人用嘅密碼","createTime":"2019-04-24T10:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T10:40:27.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"47253473326f8db0f2641bee1b0c43fae02cf57d","tid":1123211,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T10:34:15.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】你有冇用愛隊的名字作為網上密碼？如有，請盡早更改，因黑客已知道「秘密」。<br />\n<br />\n根據英國國家網路安全中心（NCSC）統計，現時最受網民歡迎的英超球隊名字，順序為利物浦、車路士、阿仙奴和曼聯。NCSC披露，多達280723帳戶使用Liverpool為密碼，成為英超隊名之冠，其次是216677次的Chelsea，僅得兩個名字超過21萬次。第3位的Arsenal使用次數，接近18萬次，第4位的manutd未超過6萬次。諷刺地，上季英超冠軍曼城的人氣不高，排名第11位。<br />\n<br />\n雖然註冊不同帳戶時，經常聽到別用太簡單的密碼，但NCSC數字顯示，以「123456」作為密碼的次數超過2320萬次，冠絕任何字符或數字的組合，可見人類總是不斷重複犯錯。<br />\n<br />\nNCSC鄭重呼籲，網民別重複使用同一組密碼，也盡量避免使用球隊名字，否則很容易被黑客破解。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"2a7e4dd5348427ac28f8674c24faa62e62cb9b05","tid":1123211,"uid":581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T10:36:17.000Z","msg":"成為英超隊名之冠<br />\n<br />\n終於攞到聯賽冠軍"},{"pid":"311f9321fc9decc9c54910791fb23c692bf7ab06","tid":1123211,"uid":215864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T10:36:22.000Z","msg":"由此可見 我利攞冠喺天意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f20990b50aa06d5e2037aebeb87d89782e46204","tid":1123211,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"311f9321fc9decc9c54910791fb23c692bf7ab06","tid":1123211,"uid":215864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T10:36:22.000Z","msg":"由此可見 我利攞冠喺天意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T10:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/246ec57d559f53bebfe99b1da354727b/tumblr_pqb57fZfhW1s4foy8_400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F246ec57d559f53bebfe99b1da354727b%2Ftumblr_pqb57fZfhW1s4foy8_400.jpg&h=2d23a8df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}